<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT52">
<l>vilaikkāṭ paṭuvar vicātiyēṟ ṟuṇpar</l>
<l>talaikkāṭ palitirivar takkōr  mulaikkāl</l>
<l>viṭamuṇṭa vēntaṉaiyē vēṟāvēt tātār</l>
<l>kaṭamuṇṭār kallā tavar.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Worthy people will become devoted servants for a price,</l>
<l>accept [and] receive [others’] diseases, [and] turn themselves</l>
<l rend="indent">into human sacrificial gifts so that [someone else protects their] head!</l>
<l>Those who do not extol the King who drank poison from [Pūtanā’s] breasts</l>
<l rend="indent">as being distinguished</l>
<l>Are ignorant people who experience sins.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
